# Automatically enter the Nix dev shell when you cd into this directory.
# Requires: direnv (https://direnv.net) + nix-direnv
#
# First-time setup:
#   echo 'eval "$(direnv hook fish)"' >> ~/.config/fish/config.fish
#   direnv allow
#
# After that, entering this directory automatically activates the shell
# with Rust, cargo-watch, etc. — no manual `nix develop` needed.

use flake
